<div class="container-fluid w-full mx-0 p-0 my-2">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8">
        <h1 class="text-center mb-5">Welcome to PetRent – Your Go-To Platform for Pet Rentals!</h1>
        <div class="row align-items-center">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <%= image_tag 'hero.jpg' , alt: 'PetRent hero image' , class: 'img-fluid' %>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <p class='fs-5 text'>
              Looking for a unique companion to enhance your photoshoot, event, or special day?
              With PetRent, you can rent a wide variety of animals, from playful dogs to majestic horses,
              and even cute little hamsters! Whether it's for a photoshoot, a birthday party, or a creative event,
              our platform connects you with pet owners who are eager to share their lovable companions for an
              unforgettable
              experience.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

        <div class="row justify-content-center my-5">
          <div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8">
            <h4 class="mb-4 fw-bolder">How It Works:</h4>
            <div class="row">
              <ul class="list-unstyled row">
                <li class="col-md-6 fs-5 text">
                  <strong>For Pet Owners:</strong> Have a photogenic or well-behaved pet you'd like to share?
                  Post a listing with photos, a description of your pet, and available rental times.
                  You set the price and terms, and even offer delivery if you'd like!
                </li>
                <li class="col-md-6 fs-5 text">
                  <strong>For Renters:</strong> Browse through a diverse selection of pets, read detailed descriptions,
                  and find the perfect animal for your event. Submit a rental request and get ready to
                  create amazing memories with your new furry, feathered, or scaly friend.
                </li>
              </ul>             
            </div>
             <p class="d-flex fs-5 text">
                Whether you're looking for a playful puppy for an hour or a majestic horse for a day,
                PetRent makes it easy to find the perfect companion for your next project.
              </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container my-5 fs-5 text">
          <div class="hero-img">
              <h4 class="fw-bolder">Why Choose PetRent?</h4>
              <ul class="list-group w-75 m-auto">
                  <li class="mb-3 list-group-item">
                      Wide Variety of Animals – From small pets like hamsters to large animals like horses,
                      there's a perfect match for every need.
                  </li>
                  <li class="mb-3 list-group-item">
                      Flexible Rental Options – Choose from hourly or daily rentals depending on your event or project.
                  </li>
                  <li class="mb-3 list-group-item">
                      Convenient Delivery – Some pet owners offer delivery services right to your location, making the process
                      hassle-free.
                  </li>
              </ul>             
          </div>           
        </div>

        <p class="row justify-content-center fs-5">
          Book your next furry, feathery, or scaly companion today and make your event one to remember with PetRent!
        </p>

    </div>
  </div>